            <li><b>Ogata, K.</b> &mdash; Modern Control Engineering, inverted-pendulum state-feedback example. Pearson.</li>
            <li><b>Virtual Labs (IIT)</b> &mdash; Control Systems: Inverted Pendulum Stabilisation, vlabs.ac.in.</li>
          </ul></div>
        </section>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
